<template>
<User_list msg="Welcome to Your Vue.js App" />
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
const baseUrl = 'http://localhost:3000/todos/'

export default {
    name: 'App',
    data() {
        return {
            todos: []
        }
    },
    methods: {
        async GetApi(){
          await axios.get(baseUrl).then((resp)=>{this.todos = resp.data;}).catch((err)=>{console.log(err);});
        }
    }
}
</script>
